item.description:
@Soull3sss1 wrote:

Soulcist:

I really only looked at the media so I’m going to ask here. What is the stability of Castlewars? I personally have ventured in the status pages of here and others to see if a server actually had a decent or more stable Castlewars than I’ve seen in others.

Very Great actually, everything works properly as it is supposed to, any bugs found i haven’t so far, so from my perspective is it best to none.
THanks for asking though
-Tyler (Freedompeace)
